data.description: This fabulous pool home located on a private wooded lot has the WOW factor you have been looking for. Discriminating buyers will appreciate the BEAUTIFUL AND SMART UPDATES in this GL Homes Rialto model.  Improvements include: *New heating and cooling system with UV filter and special condensate pump * Whole house generator *New pool heat pump * New engineered wood flooring * New gourmet kitchen with refreshed cabinets, quartz countertops, pull out drawers, new stainless appliances including a double convection oven, 4 door French refrigerator and more! * Whole house water filtration and softener system including reverse osmosis * New contemporary lighting and fans * Plantation shutters throughout * Freshy painted interior * Expanded garage storage * Newly sealed driveway and pool deck * New landscaping and curbing. This wonderfully maintained home has a great split floorplan and a spacious owners retreat with two walk-in closets with built-ins, en-suite bathroom, a large shower with a new two-way door, split vanities with makeup area, w/c with comfort height commode and lots of natural light. A dedicated living room, family room and dining room provides a space for everything. Your new home creates a comfortable Florida vibe throughout. Whether you are hosting or just hanging out, you will love living here.  Valencia Lakes has the resort lifestyle of your dreams. Bring the golf cart. The clubhouse is only a block away and local cart paths provide access to many stores and area facilities. Located just a short drive to Tampa, Sarasota, beaches, and airports too.
